where you grew up.)

568
00:33:39,710 --> 00:33:41,920
(To see if the stars there shine)

569
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:45,160
(as brightly as your eyes.)

570
00:33:46,510 --> 00:33:50,360
(I once wanted to go
to the school you studied at.)

571
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:53,230
(To see if the tall trees there stand)

572
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:56,550
(as straight as your character.)

573
00:33:58,710 --> 00:33:59,360
(Could I go?)

574
00:34:01,710 --> 00:34:02,360
(I couldn't.)

575
00:34:05,950 --> 00:34:06,950
(I wanted to say,)

576
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:11,990
