the rest of my life with you,)

577
00:34:11,990 --> 00:34:13,520
(without fearing death.)

578
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:15,390
(But)

579
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:19,520
(I'm selfish.)

580
00:34:21,390 --> 00:34:24,310
(I only wanted to share with you)

581
00:34:24,310 --> 00:34:28,080
(the joys and the triumphs.)

582
00:34:29,390 --> 00:34:30,830
(As for illness and aging,)

583
00:34:31,710 --> 00:34:35,600
(I chose to endure them alone.)

584
00:34:38,960 --> 00:34:40,910
(I don't want you)

585
00:34:41,230 --> 00:34:43,310
